    <item>
      <title>中国央行通过增加临时回购来加强对利率的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/pboc-to-conduct-temporary-repos-depending-on-market-conditions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着政策制定者扩大引导市场的工具范围，中国人民银行加强了对利率的控制，引入了影响短期借贷成本的新机制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/pboc-to-conduct-temporary-repos-depending-on-market-conditions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 00:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国大选中左翼政党意外获胜 投资者紧张不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/markets-may-warm-to-french-result-after-initial-shock-analysts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国股市周一上涨，因为该国议会选举中最糟糕的情况已经避免。但投资者和交易员警告称，由于政治僵局迫在眉睫，未来几周和几个月市场将出现动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/markets-may-warm-to-french-result-after-initial-shock-analysts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:26:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员努力应对选举结果变化，法国股市反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-quoted-lower-as-left-wing-bloc-set-to-win-french-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国大选未能产生明显赢家，这让投资者感到些许宽慰，他们猜测，在政府陷入僵局的情况下，不太可能出现重大政策变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-quoted-lower-as-left-wing-bloc-set-to-win-french-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 19:15:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗和摩根大通青睐大额债券，CPI 数据公布前获得提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/wall-street-s-big-bond-bet-revives-before-pivotal-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些华尔街最大的银行表示，债券交易将在 2024 年剩余时间内占据主导地位，而关键的通胀数据将决定该赌注的命运，在此之前，债券交易正变得越来越活跃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/wall-street-s-big-bond-bet-revives-before-pivotal-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
